if the two files were in the same folder ,you should only use it just like this:
the struct is like this :1/index=1/js->2/jquery.js.
so when you wanna use the 2 index ,you only do it like this:
<script src="js/jquery.js"></script>
what u should pay the great attention is the suffix </script>,it should never be ignored or unvalide;


and the preffix you should do is to load the content of the js file,so you should doit like this :
$(document).ready(function(){
/**********ur coding content;
});


